Equal odds [26] requires independence of ğ‘Œ and ğ‘† conditional on
ground truth labels ğ‘Œ â€” in this case it requires that each labelâ€™s
false positive and false negative rates are independent of ğ‘ğ´ğ´ğ¸ . This
